rivalry with him.</i>

20
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:09,218
What about Hunt? Has he changed?

21
00:02:09,219 --> 00:02:10,759
No, he's going on wets.

22
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,728
<i>I don't know why it
became such a big thing.</i>

23
00:02:13,729 --> 00:02:18,269
