each other's balls.</i>

24
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:20,468
<i>To me this is perfectly normal,</i>

25
00:02:20,469 --> 00:02:22,699
<i>but other people saw
it differently,</i>

26
00:02:22,699 --> 00:02:26,199
