32
00:03:23,629 --> 00:03:26,329
I think the racetrack telephoned
ahead that I was coming.

33
00:03:26,329 --> 00:03:28,170
Hunt. James Hunt.

34
00:03:32,610 --> 00:03:36,209
What's the matter? No one ever
seen a spot of blood before?

35
00:03:36,210 --> 00:03:38,969
- Are you all right?
- Absolutely fine.

36
