- It was a nasty blow.

46
00:04:08,539 --> 00:04:10,639
Done with a bloody crowbar.

47
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:14,278
- Why? What did you do?
- Nothing.

48
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,939
Only what she asked me to do.

49
