you if you like.

51
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,358
Sorry.

52
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:33,168
<i>I have a theory why women
like racing drivers.</i>

53
00:04:33,170 --> 00:04:35,939
<i>It's not because they
respect what we do,</i>

54
00:04:35,939 --> 00:04:38,439
