<i>and they're probably right.</i>

57
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:44,930
<i>It's our closeness to death.</i>

58
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:48,978
<i>The closer you are to death,
the more alive you feel.</i>

59
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:52,588
<i>The more alive you are. And
they can see that in you.</i>

60
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:54,579
