61
00:04:55,189 --> 00:04:57,528
<i>My name is James Hunt.</i>

62
00:04:57,529 --> 00:04:59,658
<i>My father is a stockbroker,</i>

63
00:04:59,659 --> 00:05:01,759
<i>my sister is a barrister</i>

64
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:04,369
<i>and my brother is an accountant.</i>

65
00:05:04,370 --> 00:05:05,918
<i>And I,</i>

66
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:08,449
<i>well, I do this.</i>

67
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:14,209
<i>It's a wonderful way to live.
It's the only way to drive.</i>

68
00:05:14,209 --> 00:05:17,009
<i>As if each day is your last.</i>

69
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,559
I've never been to a
Grand Prix before.

70
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,218
You still haven't.

71
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:33,129
- This is Formula 3.
- What's that?

72
00:05:33,490 --> 00:05:35,959
That's a lower division,

73
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:38,728
where idiots like me mess about

74
00:05:38,730 --> 00:05:42,098
in the hop of being
talent-spotted to race in F1.

75
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:44,269
- You look disappointed.
- No.

76
00:05:44,269 --> 00:05:47,439
You only slept with me because
you thought I was famous.

77
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:49,139
That's not true!

78
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,949
Don't worry. I will be one day.

79
00:05:51,949 --> 00:05:53,348
Morning, everyone.

80
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:55,319
- This is Nursie.
- Gemma.

81
00:05:55,579 --> 00:05:58,619
