Clay Regazzoni."

475
00:28:55,930 --> 00:28:58,259
You are family and friend
to the commendatore

476
00:28:58,259 --> 00:28:59,598
as long as you win.

477
00:28:59,599 --> 00:29:01,199
The minute you
don't, ciao, ciao.

478
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:02,699
I totally understand.

479
00:29:02,700 --> 00:29:04,098
It's business.

480
00:29:04,099 --> 00:29:05,509
I would do the same.

481
00:29:05,509 --> 00:29:07,709
But it isn't just
business, is it?

482
00:29:07,710 --> 00:29:10,338
What we do. It's passion, love.

483
00:29:10,339 --> 00:29:13,308
Which is why we are prepared
to risk our lives for it.

484
00:29:13,309 --> 00:29:14,348
Not me.

485
00:29:14,349 --> 00:29:16,519
If I had more talent and
