487
00:29:18,990 --> 00:29:20,989
How do you know you
will make money here?

488
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:22,659
You haven't yet.

489
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:24,849
Not yet, but I will.

490
00:29:25,430 --> 00:29:28,019
If you can, I can.

491
00:29:31,259 --> 00:29:34,200
You know, are you
ever not an asshole?

492
00:29:34,529 --> 00:29:36,538
- Why am I an asshole?
- Well...

493
00:29:36,539 --> 00:29:40,108
By now I'm both quicker than you
and better at setting up a car.

494
00:29:40,109 --> 00:29:42,378
